OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPartly
OL,6,Fcloudy this evening with showers, some
OL,7,Fheavy and thundery at first. Most
OL,8,Fshowers will die out in the early
OL,9,Fhours, the best of the clearer spells
OL,10,Ffor Argyll.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FA mainly dry and partly cloudy
OL,13,Fmorning. Sunny spells will develop
OL,14,Fduring the day alongside a few
OL,15,Fshowers, some of which may be on the
OL,16,Fheavy side.
OL,17,
OL,18,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FRain
OL,19,For showers on Tuesday and Wednesday,
OL,20,Foccasionally heavy. Drier on Thursday.
OL,21,FWarmer than of late.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
